- support capturing of a pure string:
  p({}, function() {
    "hi"
  })
- indentation
- compilation of templates
- support all html4, xhtml strict/compliant tags
- "pretty" syntax: (remove javascript cruft)

  ul foo:'bar' {
    li {
      p {
        "hi"
      }
    }
  }

  =>

  ul({foo:'bar'}, function() {
    li({}) {
      p({}, function() {
        "hi"
      })
    }
  })
